TITLE: Removing Custom Widget Group from Elementor Context Menu
DESCRIPTION: This code removes the 'custom-widget-actions' group from the widgets context menu in Elementor. It uses the 'elements/context-menu/groups' filter hook to find and splice out the specific group.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elementor/elementor-developers-docs/blob/master/src/context-menu/remove-group.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
elementor.hooks.addFilter( 'elements/context-menu/groups', ( customGroups, elementType ) => {

	if ( 'widget' === elementType ) {
		const groupIndex = customGroups.findIndex( ( group ) => 'custom-widget-actions' === group.name );
		if ( groupIndex > -1 ) {
			customGroups.splice( groupIndex, 1 );
		}
	}

	return customGroups;

} );
```

