TITLE: Adding External Link Action to Widget Context Menu
DESCRIPTION: Creates a new action that adds an external link to Elementor website in the widget context menu. The action is added to the 'custom-widget-actions' group and opens the Elementor website in a new tab.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elementor/elementor-developers-docs/blob/master/src/context-menu/add-new-action.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
elementor.hooks.addFilter( 'elements/context-menu/groups', ( customGroups, elementType ) => {

	const newAction = {
		name: 'elementor-link',
		icon: 'eicon-alert',
		title: 'Elementor Link',
		isEnabled: () => true,
		callback: () => window.open( 'https://elementor.com/', '_blank' ).focus(),
	};

	if ( 'widget' === elementType ) {
		customGroups.forEach( ( group ) => {
			if ( 'custom-widget-actions' === group.name ) {
				group.actions.push( newAction );
			}
		} );
	}

	return customGroups;

} );
```

